high_descs: Turn right and go straight and then walk to the left side of the toilet.
Pick up the soap dispenser on the toilet tank.
Walk around the toilet and straight to the sinks.
Place the soap dispenser on the counter between the two sinks.
Turn right and walk to the end of the counter.
Take the soap dispenser out of the bin on the floor.
Walk left back to the end of the sinks.
Place the soap dispenser on the counter behind the other one.
anns.task_desc: Place two soap dispensers on a counter.

high_descs: Go straight, make a right, and head towards the left side of the toilet.
Pick up the jar with a gold dispenser that is on top of the toilet.
Turn around and head towards the left-most sink.
Place the jar in between the two sinks.
Turn to the right and head towards the trash can on the left, on the floor next to the sinks.
Take the identical jar out of the trash can.
Turn around and head back to the sink.
Place the jar behind the first jar, in between the two sinks.
anns.task_desc: Fetch two jars and place them between two sinks.

high_descs: Walk to the shower, turn right and follow the curve of the shower until you are between the shower and toilet, facing the toilet.
Pick up the gold lotion container from the back of the toilet.
Carry the container to the vanity to stand in front of the leftmost sink.
Place the container on the counter between the two sinks.
Turn right and move to the trash bin to the right of the vanity.
Pick up the lotion container from inside the trash bin.
Carry the container to return to stand in front of the leftmost sink.
Place the lotion container on the counter between the two sinks.
anns.task_desc: Move two lotion containers to the counter between the sinks.
